Name: Maya Site of Copán
Description: Maya Site of Copán - UNESCO World Heritage Site. Remains of a major Maya city known for its stelae and altars, featuring some of the finest examples of Maya art and architecture.

Name: Río Plátano Biosphere Reserve
Description: Río Plátano Biosphere Reserve - UNESCO World Heritage Site. A protected area with diverse wildlife and some of the largest remnants of tropical forest in Central America.
